response.original_title: The CS2 Major Run No One Thought Was Possible
response.overview: Faze, a team in an endless slump, enter the StarLadder Budapest Major with a new unproven team. They go on to pull off an unbelievable major run, making it all the way to the final. This is the story of how it happened.
response.tagline: This is a story of how Faze, a team in a slump, manage to pull of an incredible run to the final of the StarLadder Budapest Major.
response.title: The CS2 Major Run No One Thought Was Possible
